  <brief_title>Role of Bladder Training During Post-operative Hospital Stay After Radical Hysterectomy in Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Role of Bladder Training During Post-operative Hospital Stay After Radical Hysterectomy in Patients: a Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
